  <div class="about_wrapper relative inset-0 overflow-hidden flex flex-col">
    <q class="quote relative italic"
      >Embrace challenges to predict and create your future.</q
    >
    <div class="details_wrapper relative">
      <p class="test">
        I'm all about crafting web experiences that not only meet but exceed
        expectations. Through collaboration and communication, I thrive to
        witness visions come to life.
      </p>

